    <item>
      <title>Sometimes all you need is someone to tell you that you can 🙌🏻 I try to be that v...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/CeOFP4LvUk1/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/500464018_1223781726005771_9016329210139781255_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s640x640_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=109&amp;ig_cache_key=Mjg1MDIzODY5NTUyMzMwNTc4MQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjcyMHgxMjgwLnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=8tNrTOZNyVcQ7kNvwHY1ffS&amp;_nc_oc=AdoaqJIp0y-KbBUe41bHtZEvNV8wIjam31ru2Ye-qUNEQmCkQu6QwJ-KGrl3DaZ3L3s&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=nMLNATSvp4rvtkP2KOceZA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afy-sywtKzAK_CiuHaIhDE1QZmT0iWvbWcnfnpgqOh7MUw&amp;oe=69C8E69B" alt="Instagram billede fra @emmanoa________" /></p><p><strong>@emmanoa________</strong></p><p>Sometimes all you need is someone to tell you that you can 🙌🏻<br/>
<br/>
I try to be that voice of encouragement for others, but sometimes forget that I need to hear it too. Leo is one of those voices for me. A few days ago I told him that I was far from getting these transitions. He gently told me he didn’t think I was and asked me to try. I got it first attempt. <br/>
<br/>
So so much of the yoga practice is learning when to listen to or ignore that little voice in your mind. Self-belief is so important, and someone reminding you what you are capable of is part of the magic of practicing yoga and finding the teacher who resonates with you. <br/>
<br/>
Thanks for your support and encouraging voice always and always @leo_oppenheim And thanks for co-creating at @skyhutretreats this past week. I am so grateful for it all. <br/>
<br/>
If you get a chance and are interested to practice with him he teaches in-person and online classes and upcoming retreats in- and outside of the UK, and I am exited to co-create more together in the future.</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/500464018_1223781726005771_9016329210139781255_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s640x640_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=109&amp;ig_cache_key=Mjg1MDIzODY5NTUyMzMwNTc4MQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjcyMHgxMjgwLnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=8tNrTOZNyVcQ7kNvwHY1ffS&amp;_nc_oc=AdoaqJIp0y-KbBUe41bHtZEvNV8wIjam31ru2Ye-qUNEQmCkQu6QwJ-KGrl3DaZ3L3s&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=nMLNATSvp4rvtkP2KOceZA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afy-sywtKzAK_CiuHaIhDE1QZmT0iWvbWcnfnpgqOh7MUw&amp;oe=69C8E69B" alt="Instagram billede fra @emmanoa________" /></p><p><strong>@emmanoa________</strong></p><p>Sometimes all you need is someone to tell you that you can 🙌🏻<br/>
<br/>
I try to be that voice of encouragement for others, but sometimes forget that I need to hear it too. Leo is one of those voices for me. A few days ago I told him that I was far from getting these transitions. He gently told me he didn’t think I was and asked me to try. I got it first attempt. <br/>
<br/>
So so much of the yoga practice is learning when to listen to or ignore that little voice in your mind. Self-belief is so important, and someone reminding you what you are capable of is part of the magic of practicing yoga and finding the teacher who resonates with you. <br/>
<br/>
Thanks for your support and encouraging voice always and always @leo_oppenheim And thanks for co-creating at @skyhutretreats this past week. I am so grateful for it all. <br/>
<br/>
If you get a chance and are interested to practice with him he teaches in-person and online classes and upcoming retreats in- and outside of the UK, and I am exited to co-create more together in the future.</p>]]></content:encoded>
